ScrumBook is light weight cross platform tool to handle your daily scrums and keep track of your team's progress.
Written with Ruby with help of Tk library.

Features:
  * Open/Save project to file
    * Saved file is human readable YAML format
  * Burn down chart
  * Open file that is given as argument
  * Easy to create new task to sprint
  * Easy update of tasks
  * Easy navigation between sprints
  * One click coping of open tasks to new sprint
